I reviewed the metric and trace evidence: IG01 shows an immediate, high-severity CPU I/O-wait spike at 2021-03-04 18:00:00 (UTC+8) and IG01-originating traces show coincident high-latency spikes impacting downstream Tomcat services. No contradicting logs were found in the window. Based on metric + trace alignment, the most probable single root cause is IG01 with a disk I/O-related issue.

